node.text:
One month into the circuit breaker and we have seen that the bonds between both our sons are now much stronger, in a good and bad way 😂
.
I am also really really glad that I #buybuybuy the toys nonstop previously on taobao, shoppee and ikea so we can survive together at home on days like these🤣🤭
.
.
#circuitbreakersg #YeoBabyEvan #YeoBabyEden
Hahaha i still can't get over the last video 😂
